oad" data-gemlang="en" width="100" height="21" data-width="30%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="100" natural-height="21" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709741681734" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709741681734"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">"Handgemacht, liebevoll verpackt, einzigartig – ein Geschenk, das lange bleibt. Und besser als alles, was ich vorher verschenkt habe."</span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">- Susanne L.</span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709741681703" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709741681703" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Fazit: Ist MeerglasLiebe™ das perfekte Geschenk?</h2></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709741681715" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709741681715" data-resolution="480x480"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/9fabe510-68b3-4212-9455-5132390b25fb/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/ADVERTORIAL%20MAIN%20-%202025-07-15T015041.302.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="480"